#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewporttexture.rst:19
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Displays the content of a :ref:`Viewport <class_Viewport>` node as a "
"dynamic :ref:`Texture2D <class_Texture2D>`. This can be used to mix "
"controls, 2D, and 3D elements in the same scene."
msgstr ""
"将 :ref:`Viewport <class_Viewport>` 节点的内容，显示为动态 :ref:`Texture "
"<class_Texture>`。这可用于在同一场景中混合控件、2D和3D元素。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewporttexture.rst:21
msgid ""
"To create a ViewportTexture in code, use the :ref:`Viewport.get_texture "
"<class_Viewport_method_get_texture>` method on the target viewport."
msgstr ""
"要用代码创建 ``ViewportTexture``，请在目标视图上使用 :ref:`Viewport.get_texture "
"<class_Viewport_method_get_texture>` 方法。"

